<form class="search-field" data-search-form role="search">
  <label for="blog-search">全文搜索</label>
  <div class="search-field__control">
    <input
      id="blog-search"
      type="search"
      name="q"
      maxlength="120"
      autocomplete="off"
      placeholder="搜索标题、摘要和文章正文"
      aria-describedby="blog-search-guidance blog-search-runtime"
      data-search-input
    />
    <button type="submit">搜索</button>
  </div>
  <p id="blog-search-guidance" class="search-field__guidance" data-search-guidance>
    正式构建使用 Pagefind 中文全文索引；开发服务器提供标题、摘要和标签的轻量预览。
  </p>
  <p id="blog-search-runtime" class="search-field__runtime" data-search-runtime aria-live="polite"></p>
</form>

<style>
  .search-field {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  label {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 750;
  }

  .search-field__control {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  input,
  button {
    min-height: 2.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface-strong) 92%, transparent);
  }

  input {
    width: 100%;
    padding-inline: var(--space-4);
  }

  button {
    padding-inline: var(--space-5);
    font-weight: 750;
  }

  .search-field__guidance,
  .search-field__runtime {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
  }

  .search-field__runtime:empty {
    display: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 31.99rem) {
    .search-field__control {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
